{"tid":1532970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈建議First Aid救人既同時問定傷者叫咩名同電話","createTime":"2019-09-02T15:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T16:57:16.000Z","uid":136883,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c4a22c9740d1f183226be00b9bb228ff055b73db","tid":1532970,"uid":136883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"各位而家親眼所見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算有記者first aid接近即將被捕人士，都會被逼走至防線出面，而條線係你根本無可能正常影到或者聽到佢講咩，有時現場實在嘈得太大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記者因為有鏡頭同要照顧觀眾未必可以以最接近距離，第一時間接觸到被即將拘捕既人，所以first aid要趁未比人趕走既情況下，一接近到就要問定咩名同電話，以免被逼走完全做唔到事留係原地喊，可以嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587610a7c07b01ddfaca0f20f373ea634c4272fe","tid":1532970,"uid":132497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"希望有人幫手統籌<br />\n<br />\n[創舉] 10月1日，香港人要搞個健力士世界紀錄<br />\n<br />\n如果個日全香港人舉唔同國家既國旗，唯獨是無中共垃圾旗，搞個健力士世界紀錄，有無得諗<br />\n<br />\n香港人要入健力士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落佢鬼國面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Record breaking] Oct 1, HongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<br />\n<br />\nIf all the HongKongers carry different countries national flags, except the one of CCP, and break a Guiness World Record, sound good?<br />\n<br />\nHongKongers need to break a Guiness World Record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLose ChiNazi&rsquo;s face<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532234</a>"},{"pid":"69899a554fd419f4787f8e22db25514bbc899b5e","tid":1532970,"uid":136883,"like":0,"dislike":0,